"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?33/61/34770/abstract/9\">",
"      Schobel HP, Frank H, Naraghi R, et al. Hypertension in patients with neurovascular compression is associated with increased central sympathetic outflow. J Am Soc Nephrol 2002; 13:35.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
