"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?33/61/34770/abstract/11\">",
"      Hohenbleicher H, Schmitz SA, Koennecke HC, et al. Neurovascular contact and blood pressure response in young, healthy, normotensive men. Am J Hypertens 2002; 15:119.",
